cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.HC 

The paper deals with action recognition and quality assessment, which are core topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of multitask learning (MTL) is a key aspect of the paper, which is also a popular topic in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also uses a large dataset of diving samples, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the potential applications of their approach in human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
